This paper deals with recommender systems, which are commonly studied in the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. The paper also involves modeling the problem as a subgraph selection problem, which is a common topic in the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category. The paper also discusses the complexity of the problem, which is a common topic in the Computational Complexity (cs.CC) sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves the use of algorithms and optimization techniques, which are commonly studied in the Data Structures (cs.DS) and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) sub-categories.
